article.headline: Ajayi's 16 lead Pepperdine over William & Mary 71-59
article.description: — Michael Ajayi scored 16 points as Pepperdine beat William & Mary 71-59 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Ajayi's 16 lead Pepperdine over William & Mary 71-59
article.story: MALIBU, Calif. -- — Michael Ajayi scored 16 points as Pepperdine beat William & Mary 71-59 on Thursday night. Ajayi added 12 rebounds for the Waves (6-8). Boubacar Coulibaly scored 13 points and added 13 rebounds and three blocks. Malik Moore was 6 of 12 shooting to finish with 13 points. Matteus Case finished with 15 points for the Tribe (5-7). William & Mary also got 15 points from Trey Moss. Chase Lowe also had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
